sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Forums UI
  participant GW as Gateway
  participant FS as forum-service
  participant US as user-service
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant AN as analytics

  UI->>GW: POST /api/forums/:id/threads
  GW->>FS: create thread
  FS->>US: verify token
  US-->>FS: userId
  FS->>DB: insert ForumThread
  FS->>AN: emit THREAD_CREATED
  FS-->>UI: thread created

  UI->>GW: POST /api/forums/:id/threads/:threadId/posts
  GW->>FS: create post
  FS->>DB: insert ForumPost
  FS->>AN: emit POST_CREATED
  FS-->>UI: post created

  UI->>GW: DELETE /api/forums/:id/threads/:threadId/posts/:postId
  GW->>FS: delete post
  FS->>DB: delete ForumPost (+cascade reactions/replies)
  FS->>AN: emit POST_DELETED
  FS-->>UI: delete ok
